### API Tests

### Environment Variables
@base_url = {{$dotenv DASHMATE_BASE_URL}}

### 1. Get all available widgets (no auth)
GET {{base_url}}/wp-json/dashmate/v1/widgets
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 2. Get widget data by ID (no auth)
GET {{base_url}}/wp-json/dashmate/v1/widgets/sample-html/data
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 3. Get widget content by widget ID (no auth)
GET {{base_url}}/wp-json/dashmate/v1/widgets/content/sample-html
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 4. Test if WordPress REST API is working at all
GET {{base_url}}/wp-json/wp/v2/posts
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 5. Test if your plugin namespace is registered
GET {{base_url}}/wp-json/dashmate/v1
Content-Type: application/json

###
